# TROUBLESHOOTING:
# ================
#
# 1. Check if SecretProviderClass is created:
#    kubectl get secretproviderclass dbc-azure-kv-secrets
#
# 2. Check if secrets are synced:
#    kubectl get secret dbc-postgres-credentials-synced
#
# 3. Check CSI driver logs:
#    kubectl logs -n kube-system -l app=secrets-store-csi-driver
#
# 4. Check pod events:
#    kubectl describe pod <database-configurator-pod>
#
# 5. Verify Key Vault access:
#    - Check managed identity has correct role assignments
#    - Check federated credential subject matches service account
#    - Check Key Vault firewall rules (if private endpoint)
#
# DEPLOYMENT:
# ===========
